<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Sofia | AI Engineer Portfolio</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Space+Grotesk:wght@300;500;700&family=Fira+Code:wght@400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        :root {
            --primary-glow: #bc13fe;
            --secondary-glow: #420264;
            --text-main: #f3e8ff;
            --glass-bg: rgba(25, 10, 40, 0.7);
            --border-color: rgba(188, 19, 254, 0.3);
        }

        * {
            box-sizing: border-box;
            cursor: default;
        }

        body {
            background: radial-gradient(circle at top right, #2d0b5a, #0d0216);
            background-attachment: fixed;
            color: var(--text-main);
            font-family: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            overflow-x: hidden;
        }

        /* Animated Background Particles Effect */
        body::before {
            content: "";
            position: fixed;
            top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%;
            background-image: 
                radial-gradient(white, rgba(255,255,255,0.2) 2px, transparent 40px),
                radial-gradient(white, rgba(255,255,255,0.15) 1px, transparent 30px);
            background-size: 550px 550px, 350px 350px;
            background-position: 0 0, 40px 60px;
            opacity: 0.1;
            z-index: -1;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 1100px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 60px 20px;
        }

        /* Hero Section */
        header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 80px;
            animation: fadeIn 1.5s ease;
        }

        .glitch-name {
            font-size: 4.5rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin: 0;
            background: linear-gradient(to right, #fff, var(--primary-glow));
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            letter-spacing: -2px;
        }

        .badge {
            display: inline-block;
            background: var(--primary-glow);
            color: white;
            padding: 5px 15px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            font-weight: 500;
            margin-top: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(188, 19, 254, 0.4);
        }

        /* Section Styling */
        .glass-panel {
            background: var(--glass-bg);
            backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
            border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
            border-radius: 24px;
            padding: 40px;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            transition: transform 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.175, 0.885, 0.32, 1.275);
        }

        .glass-panel:hover {
            transform: scale(1.02);
            border-color: var(--primary-glow);
            box-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(188, 19, 254, 0.1);
        }

        h2 {
            font-family: 'Fira Code', monospace;
            color: var(--primary-glow);
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            margin-top: 0;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
        }

        h2::before {
            content: "> ";
            opacity: 0.6;
        }

        /* Project Grid */
        .grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
            gap: 25px;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        .project-card {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 18px;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .project-card::after {
            content: "";
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 0; right: 0;
            width: 40px; height: 40px;
            background: var(--primary-glow);
            opacity: 0.1;
            clip-path: polygon(100% 0, 0% 100%, 100% 100%);
        }

        .tech-tag {
            font-family: 'Fira Code', monospace;
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            color: #d19bff;
            margin-right: 10px;
        }

        /* Footer Quote */
        footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 100px 20px 60px;
        }

        .quote-container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        .quote-text {
            font-style: italic;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            opacity: 0.8;
            line-height: 1.8;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .sofia-brand {
            font-weight: 700;
            letter-spacing: 12px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            color: white;
            margin-top: 30px;
        }

        @keyframes fadeIn {
            from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px); }
            to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
        }

        /* Responsive Fixes */
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .glitch-name { font-size: 3rem; }
            .glass-panel { padding: 25px; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="container">
    <header>
        <div class="glitch-name">SOFIA</div>
        <div class="badge">AI ENGINEERING CANDIDATE</div>
        <p style="margin-top: 20px; opacity: 0.6; font-family: 'Fira Code';">System.Status: <span style="color: #00ffaa;">Operational</span></p>
    </header>

    <div class="glass-panel">
        <h2>Mission Statement</h2>
        <p>Expertly navigating the intersection of <b>Artificial Intelligence</b> and <b>Physical Robotics</b>. I specialize in developing intelligent systems using Python and Java, currently focusing on autonomous logic and interactive digital narratives.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="glass-panel">
        <h2>Technical Arsenal</h2>
        <div class="grid">
            <div>
                <h3>Core Stack</h3>
                <p><span class="tech-tag">#Python</span> <span class="tech-tag">#Java</span> <span class="tech-tag">#C++</span></p>
            </div>
            <div>
                <h3>Robotics & Dev</h3>
                <p><span class="tech-tag">#Arduino</span> <span class="tech-tag">#RenPy</span> <span class="tech-tag">#mBlock</span></p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="glass-panel">
        <h2>Primary Operations</h2>
        <div class="grid">
            <div class="project-card">
                <h3>Project "Ren"</h3>
                <p>A complex visual novel engine built on Python, featuring dynamic decision branching and custom UI logic.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="project-card">
                <h3>Robotic Prototypes</h3>
                <p>Developing sensor-integrated autonomous systems using Arduino and C++ for real-world environmental interaction.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <footer>
        <div class="quote-container">
            <p class="quote-text">"The only way to discover the limits of the possible is to go beyond them into the impossible."</p>
            <div style="width: 50px; height: 2px; background: var(--primary-glow); margin: 0 auto;"></div>
            <p class="sofia-brand">SOFIA 🌙</p>
            <p style="font-size: 0.7rem; letter-spacing: 2px; opacity: 0.4;">PURSUING THE IMPOSSIBLE • EST 2025</p>
        </div>
    </footer>
</div>

</body>
</html>
